  "body": "Hi,\n\nI figured out that with the current rpc call method eth_getBlockByNumber it is not possible to get all information needed for a block header.\nThere is no triehash(receipts).\n\nFor a project I need to get the block header of the pending block via rpc in order to validate the header hash later by a third party.\n\nWould be nice if you could implement this feature.\n\nThanks Philipp\n",
